ilyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5406,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/20\/resurrection-prophet-hawd-wudu\/","url_meta":{"origin":5408,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hawd: The Prophet recognizes believers at the Fountain","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 20, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, my fountain is wider than the distance between Aylah and 'Adan. Its water is whiter than ice, sweeter than honey and milk. Its cups are more numerous than the stars. Verily, I will block some\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":797,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/20\/prophet-business-yahud\/","url_meta":{"origin":5408,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Trade: The Prophet has business relations with Jews","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 20, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, passed away while his armor was mortgaged to a Jew for thirty portions of barley. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2916, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1603 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u062a\u064f\u0648\u064f\u0641\u0650\u0651\u064a\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\